      • blueprintBundles

        private @NonNull Map<GameModeAddon,List<BlueprintBundle>> blueprintBundles
        Map of blueprint bundles to game mode addon. Inner map's key is the uniqueId of the blueprint bundle so it's easy to get from a UI

      • blueprints

        private @NonNull Map<GameModeAddon,List<Blueprint>> blueprints
        Map of blueprints. There can be many blueprints per game mode addon Inner map's key is the blueprint's name so it's easy to get from a UI
